description: We are a mobile espresso bar that offers an assortment of handcrafted coffee and espresso drinks, teas, pastries and sweets.  Lucky Lab loves a good party and would be perfect for your next corporate summit/conference, employee appreciation, holiday party, birthday party or wedding!  We also offer corporate delivery (like a lunch truck) to your office park-handcrafted coffee delivered right to your office door!
name: Lucky Lab Coffee Company
